00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:13,000
he's kind of nice-looking,

597
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:14,090
knows a bit of medicine

598
00:29:14,090 --> 00:29:15,070
and martial arts,

599
00:29:15,070 --> 00:29:16,510
and owns a house and shop.

600
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,720
His wife doesn't need to serve his parents

601
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:19,960
or deal with

602
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:21,180
the sisters-in-law.

603
00:29:23,400 --> 00:29:24,350
Come to think of it,

604
00:29:24,350 --> 00:29:26,350
he's actually got great qualities.

605
00:29:26,700 --> 00:29:27,720
No wonder you like him.

606
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:28,980
Even I'm a bit tempted.

607
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:32,790
That's not why I like him.

608
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,680
It's because when I'm with him,

609
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,480
I feel at ease.

610
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,240
At ease?

611
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:44,350
No matter what I do,

612
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,700
as long as he's around,

613
00:29:46,480 --> 00:29:47,880
I don't feel afraid.

614
00:29:50,990 --> 00:29:52,650
You've really fallen for him.

615
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:56,110
Enough about me.

616
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:59,240
Your house is so big and bright.

617
00:29:59,540 --> 00:30:01,540
It must have cost quite a bit, right?

618
00:30:02,110 --> 00:30:03,720
Someone just died nearby.

619
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:04,960
It's considered a bit ominous,

620
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,220
so the rent is cheaper.

621
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:07,110
Besides,

622
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,550
it's close to the market.

623
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:09,480
So I moved in.

624
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:12,000
You're really brave.

625
00:30:13,150 --> 00:30:15,150
Every patch of land buries someone.

626
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,360
I'm not afraid at all.

627
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:18,550
You vicious tramp!

628
00:30:18,830 --> 00:30:20,590
Vicious tramp, come out!

629
00:30:20,750 --> 00:30:22,550
You vicious tramp.

630
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:24,060
You cheated and caused my second uncle's death.

631
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:25,240
Today I'm here to get justice

632
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:25,960
for my uncle!

633
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,000
That's right! Justice!

634
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:27,720
Justice!

635
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,240
I didn't cheat. I didn't!

636
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:29,840
Nonsense!

637
00:30:30,030 --> 00:30:31,320
If you hadn't cheated,

638
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:32,400
why didn't you report it

639
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,620
when my uncle went missing?

640
00:30:33,620 --> 00:30:34,630
You clearly had something to hide!

641
00:30:34,630 --> 00:30:35,240
Yeah!

642
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,700
Someone like you

643
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:38,310
should be expelled from the Zhang family!

644
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,440
Yes, expel her!

645
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,070
That's right.

646
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:42,110
A heartless,

647
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:44,020
unfaithful woman like you

648
00:30:44,170 --> 00:30:45,210
has no right

649
00:30:45,310 --> 00:30:46,840
to stay in the Zhang family!

650
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:48,300
Right! Expel her!

651
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:51,990
Everyone's watching.

652
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,790
You vicious woman,

653
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:54,920
do you admit to adultery?

654
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,750
Do you admit it?

655
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:57,070
Do you admit it? Speak up!

656
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:57,480
Speak!

657
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,160
Speak!

658
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:00,720
Just admit it.

659
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,400
Yeah, do you admit it?

660
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,270
I admit it.

661
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,270
I admit it's all my fault.

662
00:31:11,810 --> 00:31:13,890
I shouldn't have been born a woman.

663
00:31:14,830 --> 00:31:16,480
If I hadn't, maybe my husband's death

664
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,480
wouldn't have brought

665
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,160
you bullies to my doorstep!

666
00:31:19,550 --> 00:31:21,040
Watch your mouth!

667
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:23,130
What did you just say, you vile woman?

668
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,610
You all really think I don't get it?

669
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:28,410
You act all righteous,

670
00:31:29,420 --> 00:31:30,380
but you just want

671
00:31:30,410 --> 00:31:31,400
to pin a crime on me

672
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,090
and kick me out

673
00:31:32,090 --> 00:31:33,770
so you can steal my house!

674
00:31:34,090 --> 00:31:35,640
How dare you slander us?

675
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,630
You filthy tramp!

676
00:31:37,650 --> 00:31:38,960
I'll tear your mouth apart today!

677
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:40,110
-Don't!
-Hit her!

678
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,550
Hit her! Hit her!

679
00:31:41,790 --> 00:31:42,440
Back off!

680
00:31:44,990 --> 00:31:46,360
Who are you?

681
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,240
Never seen someone dumping slop before?

682
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:52,240
I said back off, but you didn't move.

683
00:31:52,300 --> 00:31:53,300
Serves you right.

684
00:31:54,110 --> 00:31:54,790
All of you ganging up

685
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:56,050
on one helpless woman—

686
00:31:56,110 --> 00:31:57,590
aren't you afraid of the law?

687
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:59,110
Don't try to scare us with the law.

688
00:31:59,110 --> 00:32:00,030
Who are you?

689
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:01,440
That's

690
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:02,720
none of your business!

691
00:32:02,750 --> 00:32:04,240
You're assaulting someone in public,

692
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:05,400
and she's hurt.

693
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,550
If you don't leave,

694
00:32:06,550 --> 00:32:08,750
I'll report this to the government now.

695
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:12,480
Fine.

696
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:14,830
You win this time.

697
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:15,790
But you two

698
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,160
can't protect her forever.

699
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:17,960
Just you wait.

700
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,000
Just you wait!

701
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:22,520
Are you okay?

702
00:32:26,350 --> 00:32:27,400
As your neighbor,

703
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:28,590
I've heard a bit

704
00:32:28,590 --> 00:32:29,850
about your situation.

705
00:32:30,510 --> 00:32:32,040
Forgive me for saying this,

706
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:33,200
but your husband

707
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,230
was an alcoholic.

708
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,480
He was rude

709
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:36,400
and violent.

710
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,480
His death

711
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,330
must be a relief for you.

712
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,540
Maybe you should report this.

713
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,920
You're all alone.

714
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:46,800
If they come back,

715
00:32:46,820 --> 00:32:47,930
what will you do?

716
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:51,930
At worst, they'll beat me to death.

717
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:53,720
Don't say such things.

718
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:55,790
Is there no justice left in this world?

719
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:57,320
You can't be afraid of them.

720
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:58,310
The more fear you show,

721
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,840
the more they'll bully you.

722
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:03,960
The Sanhuai Lane

723
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:05,160
really is cursed.

724
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,400
Banxia,

725
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,960
do you remember the man

726
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:10,880
who fell to his death the other day?

727
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:11,960
He lived here too.

728
00:33:18,210 --> 00:33:19,170
You knew him?

729
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:21,750
No.

730
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:29,810
I live right there.

731
00:33:30,710 --> 00:33:32,310
We're neighbors from now on.

732
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,710
If you need any help,

733
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:34,680
just call me.

734
00:33:36,930 --> 00:33:37,650
Thank you.

735
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:41,240
Let's go.

736
00:34:14,510 --> 00:34:15,300
You again!

737
00:34:20,610 --> 00:34:21,960
I was about to look for you,

738
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,489
yet you showed up yourself.

739
00:34:39,030 --> 00:34:40,290
Where did you get this?

740
00:34:47,590 --> 00:34:49,120
Do you really know Man Ying?

741
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,030
Yeah, I do.

742
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:53,090
Untie the rope,

743
00:34:53,239 --> 00:34:54,370
kneel down,

744
00:34:54,389 --> 00:34:55,770
and kowtow three times to me.

745
00:34:55,770 --> 00:34:57,430
Then I'll take you to find him.

746
00:35:00,290 --> 00:35:01,350
You don't know him.

747
00:35:12,180 --> 00:35:12,950
Xuanye.

748
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:16,480
Xuanye…

749
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:21,230
Then do you know Xuanye?

750
00:35:25,350 --> 00:35:26,200
You do.

751
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:28,070
Then take me to see him.

752
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:28,760
No way!

753
00:35:31,440 --> 00:35:33,640
Then I'll have no choice but to kill you.

754
00:35:34,690 --> 00:35:35,980
I don't think you will.

755
00:35:42,450 --> 00:35:43,980
I don't have much patience.

756
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:46,230
Three.

757
00:35:49,630 --> 00:35:50,190
Two.

758
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:51,860
I'll take you.

759
00:35:54,130 --> 00:35:55,260
I can take you to him,

760
00:35:56,150 --> 00:35:57,350
but after you see him,

761
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:58,480
you have to let me go.

762
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,070
Sure.

763
00:35:59,620 --> 00:36:01,280
Once I see him, I'll let you go.

764
00:36:12,590 --> 00:36:13,440
Physician Jiu isn't here.

765
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,700
Come back another day.

766
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:17,400
He's been gone for three days.

767
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:18,490
Think carefully again.

768
00:36:18,490 --> 00:36:20,090
Did he say where he was going?

769
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:33,250
Where have you been all these days?

770
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:36,150
Banxia?

771
00:36:38,270 --> 00:36:39,270
It really is you!

772
00:36:40,330 --> 00:36:40,960
Don't you recognize me?

773
00:36:40,960 --> 00:36:41,890
It's me, Li Xian.

774
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,030
Xuanye.

775
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:45,400
This is Banxia,

776
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:46,510
my fiancée.

777
00:36:53,870 --> 00:36:54,350
Sir,

778
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:55,700
madam,

779
00:36:56,750 --> 00:36:57,980
after I heard what happened to you,

780
00:36:57,980 --> 00:36:58,810
I traveled day and night

781
00:36:58,810 --> 00:36:59,470
to get here.

782
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,400
This is truly wonderful news.

783
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,480
Uncle Duan has returned,

784
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:04,020
and Aunt Duan has been found.

785
00:37:04,020 --> 00:37:05,320
When my father heard about it,

786
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,360
he was so happy he drank

787
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:07,690
three big bowls of wine!

788
00:37:07,830 --> 00:37:09,180
If not for his official duties,

789
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:10,580
he would've come with me.

790
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,480
It was a long journey.

791
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,000
Xian,

792
00:37:13,100 --> 00:37:14,100
you must be tired.

793
00:37:14,550 --> 00:37:15,570
Uncle, you're so kind.

794
00:37:15,570 --> 00:37:16,030
We're all

795
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,490
one family now, aren't we?

796
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:18,800
Oh, right.

797
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,960
This is Physician Jiu. His name is Xuanye.

798
00:37:22,770 --> 00:37:23,900
He saved my life.

799
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,550
My journey here

800
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,020
was full of danger—

801
00:37:27,730 --> 00:37:29,420
steep mountains,

802
00:37:29,590 --> 00:37:30,520
vicious beasts,

803
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:31,860
and wolves all around.

804
00:37:31,930 --> 00:37:33,390
I barely made it out alive.

805
00:37:34,210 --> 00:37:36,420
If it hadn't been for Xuanye,

806
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:37,550
who scared off the wolves

807
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:38,880
with his mere presence,

808
00:37:39,290 --> 00:37:40,690
this fragile body of mine

809
00:37:40,940 --> 00:37:41,920
would've disappeared

810
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,850
from this world.

811
00:37:43,630 --> 00:37:44,320
Xuanye

812
00:37:44,530 --> 00:37:45,880
is not only kind and righteous

813
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:47,140
but also clever, wise,

814
00:37:47,220 --> 00:37:48,430
well-read,

815
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:49,710
and talented.

816
00:37:50,460 --> 00:37:51,190
On our way back,

817
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:51,990
we talked about

818
00:37:51,990 --> 00:37:54,390
astrology, geography, and local customs.

819
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:56,390
We never ran out of things to say.

820
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:58,990
I truly wish we had met earlier.

821
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,330
Xian, you may not know,

822
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,670
but we've known

823
00:38:03,690 --> 00:38:05,540
Physician Jiu for some time now.

824
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:06,710
He also saved

825
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:08,840
our whole family.

826
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:10,360
What a coincidence!

827
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:11,670
Xuanye,

828
00:38:12,070 --> 00:38:13,760
I told you we were destined to meet.

829
00:38:13,760 --> 00:38:15,020
We should do as I suggested—

830
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:16,320
follow the ways of the ancients:

831
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:17,110
drink blood wine

832
00:38:17,110 --> 00:38:18,640
and become sworn brothers.

833
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:19,600
But he refused.

834
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,310
Thank you, Physician Jiu,

835
00:38:25,310 --> 00:38:26,560
for saving Li Xian.

836
00:38:28,650 --> 00:38:29,850
It's a great kindness

837
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:31,070
to both the Duan family

838
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,470
and Banxia.

839
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:36,360
You must be tired

840
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,200
after your long journey.

841
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:40,440
Why don't you go home and get some rest?

842
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,360
In a few days,

843
00:38:41,550 --> 00:38:43,480
I'll host a banquet at Yanlai Restaurant

844
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:45,670
and invite you to drink with us.

845
00:38:48,440 --> 00:38:49,570
That's a great idea.

846
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:50,480
Xuanye,

847
00:38:50,710 --> 00:38:52,230
don't turn us down then.

848
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:56,480
Okay.

849
00:38:57,380 --> 00:38:58,440
I'll head back now.

850
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,030
Yeah, Banxia,

851
00:39:05,030 --> 00:39:06,230
see Xuanye off for me.

852
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:07,360
Xuanye,

853
00:39:07,550 --> 00:39:09,610
I'll come to thank you in person soon.

854
00:39:12,320 --> 00:39:12,950
Xuanye.

855
00:39:14,110 --> 00:39:14,760
Xuanye.

856
00:39:16,220 --> 00:39:17,300
As you know,

857
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:18,880
I've already told my father

858
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,320
about breaking off the engagement,

859
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:22,030
and he was going to write to the Li family.

860
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,280
I don't know why

861
00:39:23,300 --> 00:39:24,830
Li Xian suddenly showed up.

862
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:28,830
Are you mad?

863
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:31,150
I'm not mad.

864
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:33,960
Really?

865
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,070
Really.

866
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:37,660
You should go back now.

867
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:39,400
After all, he came here for you.

868
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,460
Don't be impolite.

869
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:41,810
But...

870
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:42,800
I'm really fine.

871
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,330
Alright then.

872
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,280
I'll come see you later.

873
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:50,000
Okay.

874
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:37,950
Bodhisattva,

875
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:39,740
I'm here again.

876
00:40:41,190 --> 00:40:42,510
Lv Sanlang is dead too.

877
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,190
I think

878
00:40:44,590 --> 00:40:46,750
you must've heard my prayers

879
00:40:47,360 --> 00:40:49,000
and used your divine powers

880
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,800
to punish the wicked.

881
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,880
My life has been full of sorrow.

882
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:58,670
I married Zhang Pu at 15.

883
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:02,150
After we married,

884
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:04,170
he drank excessively every day

885
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:05,480
and beat me

886
00:41:06,140 --> 00:41:08,470
and yelled at me over the slightest thing.

887
00:41:10,700 --> 00:41:11,950
After his death,

888
00:41:13,460 --> 00:41:15,130
my neighbor Lv Sanlang

889
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:17,510
took advantage of my being alone

890
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:21,430
and often harassed me.

891
00:41:23,420 --> 00:41:25,210
I had no one to turn to,

892
00:41:25,240 --> 00:41:26,200
so I came to you.

893
00:41:28,390 --> 00:41:29,370
But I never thought

894
00:41:29,370 --> 00:41:30,850
you would really listen.

895
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:32,640
Bodhisattva,

896
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:35,200
you've already helped me twice.

897
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,480
I thought I could start

898
00:41:37,480 --> 00:41:38,960
a new life,

899
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:43,270
but why is it still not possible?

900
00:41:47,590 --> 00:41:49,280
Is it that I don't deserve

901
00:41:50,850 --> 00:41:52,940
to have happiness in this life?

902
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:55,840
If I were a man,

903
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:59,640
everything would be different, right?

904
00:42:03,020 --> 00:42:03,820
Bodhisattva,

905
00:42:04,150 --> 00:42:05,070
please help me.

906
00:42:06,150 --> 00:42:08,680
This is the last time I'm asking for your help.

907
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,190
Please show mercy.

908
00:42:11,510 --> 00:42:13,960
Being a woman is too painful.

909
00:42:14,670 --> 00:42:15,760
In my next life,

910
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,960
please let me be a man.

911
00:42:22,110 --> 00:42:22,840
Take care.

912
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:26,070
Banxia.

913
00:42:28,130 --> 00:42:29,660
Are you looking for Xuanye?

914
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:30,400
Yeah.

915
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:31,390
He's not here.

916
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:32,680
Where did he go?

917
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:33,770
He went fishing.

918
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,160
Then I'll go find him.

919
00:42:44,310 --> 00:42:45,140
Chi Xue.

920
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:46,580
Lend me your umbrella.

921
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:51,150
I don't want

922
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:53,740
my daughter involved in anything

923
00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:55,690
related to demons ever again.

924
00:42:56,230 --> 00:42:58,400
And I don't want her

925
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:01,590
to marry a demon hunter.

926
00:43:16,930 --> 00:43:18,190
Do it!

927
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:28,190
Xuanye.

928
00:43:31,800 --> 00:43:33,840
I've been looking for you.

929
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:37,920
It's going to rain,

930
00:43:38,110 --> 00:43:39,230
so I brought an umbrella

931
00:43:39,230 --> 00:43:40,030
to pick you up.

932
00:43:45,670 --> 00:43:47,170
Let's go home.

933
00:43:47,340 --> 00:43:48,040
Once it starts raining,

934
00:43:48,040 --> 00:43:49,030
it'll be hard to find shelter.

935
00:43:49,030 --> 00:43:49,710
Banxia.

936
00:43:50,920 --> 00:43:52,070
I need to talk to you.

937
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:55,030
Can't it wait

938
00:43:55,030 --> 00:43:56,420
until we get home?

939
00:43:57,230 --> 00:43:58,360
Let's go home first.

940
00:44:02,510 --> 00:44:03,710
Let's end things here.

